//award
const slider = document.getElementById("awardsSlider");
const prev = document.getElementById("awardPrev");
const next = document.getElementById("awardNext");

let autoSlide;

// Calculate width dynamically
function getCardWidth() {
  const card = slider.querySelector(".award-card");
  const gap = parseInt(getComputedStyle(slider).gap) || 0;
  return card.offsetWidth + gap;
}

function slideNext() {
  slider.scrollLeft += getCardWidth();

  if (slider.scrollLeft + slider.clientWidth >= slider.scrollWidth - 5) {
    setTimeout(() => (slider.scrollLeft = 0), 300);
  }
}

function slidePrev() {
  slider.scrollLeft -= getCardWidth();

  if (slider.scrollLeft <= 0) {
    setTimeout(() => (slider.scrollLeft = slider.scrollWidth), 300);
  }
}

next.onclick = () => {
  stopAuto();
  slideNext();
  startAuto();
};

prev.onclick = () => {
  stopAuto();
  slidePrev();
  startAuto();
};

function startAuto() {
  autoSlide = setInterval(slideNext, 2500);
}

function stopAuto() {
  clearInterval(autoSlide);
}

slider.addEventListener("mouseenter", stopAuto);
slider.addEventListener("mouseleave", startAuto);

startAuto();

let clientIndex = 0;

const track = document.getElementById("clientSliderTrack");
const cards = document.querySelectorAll(".client-review-card");
const nextBtn = document.getElementById("clientNextBtn");
const prevBtn = document.getElementById("clientPrevBtn");

function slideClientReviews() {
  const cardWidth = cards[0].offsetWidth + 24;
  track.style.transform = `translateX(-${clientIndex * cardWidth}px)`;
}

nextBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
  if (clientIndex < cards.length - 1) {
    clientIndex++;
    slideClientReviews();
  }
});

prevBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
  if (clientIndex > 0) {
    clientIndex--;
    slideClientReviews();
  }
});

/* AUTO SLIDE */
setInterval(() => {
  clientIndex = (clientIndex + 1) % cards.length;
  slideClientReviews();
}, 4000);

/* FIX ON RESIZE */
window.addEventListener("resize", slideClientReviews);
